  A production-ready logging configuration module for Python.
</p>

---

## Installation

```
pip install gadlogger
```

## Usage

```python
import json
import sys
import logging
from gadlogger import config, Logger

config.setup(Logger("root", logging.INFO, json, sys.stdout))

logger = logging.getLogger()
```
